an event is/was a ranking event.\n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\" colspan=\"4\"|RV / Ranking & Variant Format Event || means an event is/was a ranking & variant format event.\n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\" colspan=\"4\"|MR / Minor-Ranking Event || means an event is/was a minor-ranking event.\n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\" colspan=\"4\"|PA / Pro-am Event || means an event is/was a pro-am event.\n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\" colspan=\"4\"|VF / Variant Format Event || means an event is/was a variant format event.\n|}\n{{Reflist|group=nb}}\n</div>\n\n==Career finals==\n\n===Ranking finals: 7 (3 titles, 4 runners-up)===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"background:#eee;\"\n|'''Legend'''\n|- style=\"background:#e5d1cb;\"\n|  World Championship (0\u20131)\n|- bgcolor=\n|  Other (3\u20133)\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|width=\"80\"|'''Outcome'''\n|width=\"20\"|'''No.'''\n|width=\"50\"|'''Year'''\n|style=\"width:250px;\"|'''Championship'''\n|style=\"width:200px;\"|'''Opponent in the final'''\n|style=\"text-align:center; width:50px;\"|'''Score'''\n|-\n| bgcolor=\"98FB98\"|Winner\n| 1.\n| [[2012 Australian Goldfields Open|2012]]\n| [[Australian Goldfields Open]]\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Peter Ebdon]]\n| align=\"center\"|9\u20133\n|- style=\"background:#e5d1cb;\"\n| bgcolor=\"ffa07a\"|Runner-up \n| 1.\n| [[2013 World Snooker Championship|2013]]\n| [[World Snooker Championship]]\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ronnie O'Sullivan]]\n| align=\"center\"|12\u201318\n|-\n| bgcolor=\"98FB98\"|Winner\n| 2.\n| [[Players Tour Championship 2013/2014 \u2013 Finals|2014]]\n| [[Players Tour Championship Finals]]\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} [[Gerard Greene]]\n| align=\"center\"|4\u20130\n|-\n| bgcolor=\"ffa07a\"|Runner-up\n| 2.\n| [[2016 Northern Ireland Open|2016]]\n| [[Northern Ireland Open (snooker)|Northern Ireland Open]]\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mark King (snooker player)|Mark King]]\n| align=\"center\"|8\u20139\n|-\n| bgcolor=\"